<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Hobby Website</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .header-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff4500;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 80%;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #ff4500;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border: none;
        }

        /* Container for all cards */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Styling for each card */
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-left: 5px solid #2196F3; /* Default blue border */
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        /* Individual border colors for each card */
        .freefire-card { border-left-color: #ff4500; }
        .drstone-card { border-left-color: #4CAF50; }
        .rent-card { border-left-color: #E91E63; }
        .masamune-card { border-left-color: #9C27B0; }
        .bluelock-card { border-left-color: #00BCD4; }
        .cote-card { border-left-color: #3F51B5; }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header-section">
        <h1>Welcome to My Digital Notebook! 🎮🌱</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">I am learning coding using my mobile phone, and this is my first web page.</p>
        <hr class="divider">
    </div>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="card freefire-card">
            <h2 style="color: #ff4500;">My Favorite Game: Free Fire 🎯</h2>
            <p>I love to play Free Fire in my free time. It helps me improve my quick decision-making skills, which also helps me in coding!</p>
        </div>

        <h2 style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0 20px 0; color: #333;">My Favorite Anime Series 🍿🔥</h2>

        <div class="card drstone-card">
            <h2 style="color: #4CAF50;">Dr. Stone 🧪</h2>
            <p>An incredible sci-fi anime where thousands of years after the entire human race turns to stone, a genius high schooler named Senku uses the power of science to rebuild civilization from scratch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card rent-card">
            <h2 style="color: #E91E63;">Rent-a-Girlfriend 🌸</h2>
            <p>A hilarious romantic-comedy series. It follows Kazuya Kinoshita and Chizuru Mizuhara as they navigate a fake relationship full of funny misunderstandings, drama, and unexpected turns.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card masamune-card">
            <h2 style="color: #9C27B0;">Masamune-kun's Revenge 🔄</h2>
            <p>A fun story about Masamune Makabe, who completely transforms himself into a handsome student to seek revenge on his childhood bully, leading to a complex and dramatic school life.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card bluelock-card">
            <h2 style="color: #00BCD4;">Blue Lock ⚽⚡</h2>
            <p>An intense, high-hype sports anime focused on soccer. It features a revolutionary training camp where top forward players from Japan ruthlessly compete against each other to become the world's greatest striker.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card cote-card">
            <h2 style="color: #3F51B5;">Classroom of the Elite 🧠🛡️</h2>
            <p>Set in a prestigious high school where students face intense competition, this thriller centers around the brilliant and mysterious Kiyotaka Ayanokoji, who secretly manipulates events from behind the scenes.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
